== Overview ==
The 20mm Manifold cannon is tri-barreled machine gun which has double the fire power of its predecesor, the [[20mm Auto Cannon]]. Great against unshielded targets with little or no armour deflection.

== Where to Acquire ==
The 20mm Manifold cannon can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
